 be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"lessor_signature","label":"Lessor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"lessee_signature","label":"Lessee Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Lease Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the lease agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the lease agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Lease Agreement Generator - Free Online Lease Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Lease Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 6);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Cease and Desist Letter Generator', 'cease-and-desist-letter-generator', 'Create a professional cease and desist letter online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional cease and desist letter online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-bank', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"reference_number","label":"Reference Number","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"letter_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"sender","label":"From (Sender)","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"recipient","label":"To (Recipient)","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"subject","label":"Subject","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"conduct_complained_of","label":"Conduct Complained Of","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"You are engaging in conduct that infringes the rights of the sender, as more particularly described below. This conduct is unlawful and must cease immediately."},{"name":"compliance_deadline","label":"Comply By (Date)","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"consequences","label":"Consequences of Non-Compliance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If you fail to comply by the date stated above, the sender reserves all rights to pursue all available legal remedies, including injunctive relief and a claim for damages and legal costs, without further notice to you."},{"name":"body","label":"Letter Body","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This letter constitutes formal notice demanding that you immediately CEASE AND DESIST from the conduct described below. The sender takes this matter seriously and is prepared to enforce its rights to the fullest extent permitted by law. This letter is sent without prejudice to any of the sender''s rights and remedies, all of which are expressly reserved."},{"name":"closing","label":"Closing","type":"text","required":false,"default":"Yours faithfully,"},{"name":"signatory_name","label":"Signatory Name","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"signatory_title","label":"Signatory Title / Position","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"signatory_signature","label":"Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is a cease and desist letter legally binding?","a":"A cease and desist letter is a formal demand, not a court order, so it is not itself binding. However, it puts the recipient on formal written notice, often resolves the matter without litigation, and creates important evidence that you asserted your rights — which strengthens any later court claim. For serious matters, have an attorney review or send it."},{"q":"What conduct can a cease and desist letter address?","a":"It is commonly used for intellectual-property infringement (trademark, copyright), defamation, harassment, breach of contract, debt collection, and breaches of confidentiality or non-compete obligations. Describe the specific conduct and the rights infringed as clearly as possible."},{"q":"Can I download this Cease and Desist Letter as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Cease and Desist Letter suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Cease and Desist Letter Generator - Free Online Cease and Desist Letter Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Cease and Desist Letter Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 7);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Affidavit Generator', 'affidavit-generator', 'Create a professional affidavit online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional affidavit online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-bank', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"affiant","label":"Affiant","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"statement","label":"Sworn Statement","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"sworn_location","label":"Sworn/Signed At (City, State)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"notary_name","label":"Notary Public Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"notes","label":"Additional Notes","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"affiant_signature","label":"Affiant Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"notary_signature","label":"Notary Public Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Affidavit Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the affidavit tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the affidavit as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Affidavit Generator - Free Online Affidavit Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Affidavit Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 8);
