eement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the independent contractor agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Independent Contractor Agreement Generator - Free Online Independent Contractor Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Independent Contractor Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 11);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Standard Operating Procedure Generator', 'standard-operating-procedure-generator', 'Create a professional standard operating procedure online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional standard operating procedure online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"sop_title","label":"SOP Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Standard Operating Procedure"},{"name":"sop_number","label":"SOP Number","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"version","label":"Version","type":"text","required":false,"default":"1.0"},{"name":"effective_date","label":"Effective Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"department","label":"Department / Process Owner","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"purpose","label":"Purpose","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This Standard Operating Procedure defines the standard, repeatable steps for carrying out the process described, to ensure consistency, quality, safety and compliance across the organisation."},{"name":"scope","label":"Scope","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This procedure applies to the roles, departments and activities described here. Exceptions, if any, are noted."},{"name":"responsibilities","label":"Roles & Responsibilities","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The roles responsible for performing, reviewing and approving each part of this procedure are defined here."},{"name":"procedure_steps","label":"Procedure Steps","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"references","label":"References & Related Documents","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"List any policies, forms, standards or related SOPs referenced by this procedure."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"approved_by","label":"Approved By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"approved_signature","label":"Approval Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a standard operating procedure (SOP) contain?","a":"A good SOP states its purpose and scope, defines roles and responsibilities, lays out the steps in clear sequence, references related documents, and carries a version number, effective date and approval. This structure makes processes repeatable, auditable and easy to train against — and is expected under quality standards such as ISO 9001."},{"q":"Why version-control SOPs?","a":"Processes change, and everyone must follow the current version. A version number, effective date and approval record ensure people use the right procedure, support audits, and create a history of how a process has evolved."},{"q":"Can I download this Standard Operating Procedure (SOP) as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Standard Operating Procedure (SOP) suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Standard Operating Procedure Generator - Free Online Standard Operating Procedure Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Standard Operating Procedure Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 1);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Meeting Minutes Generator', 'meeting-minutes-generator', 'Create a professional meeting minutes online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional meeting minutes online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"organization_name","label":"Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"meeting_title","label":"Meeting Title","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"meeting_date","label":"Meeting Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"meeting_time","label":"Time","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"location","label":"Location / Platform","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"attendees","label":"Attendees","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"List those present, any apologies for absence, and the chair and minute-taker."},{"name":"agenda_items","label":"Agenda Items & Discussion","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"action_items","label":"Action Items & Owners","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"decisions","label":"Decisions Made","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Record the key decisions reached, including any votes and outcomes."},{"name":"next_meeting","label":"Next Meeting Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"minutes_prepared_by","label":"Minutes Prepared By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"chair_signature","label":"Chairperson Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should professional meeting minutes capture?","a":"Effective minutes record the date, attendees and apologies, the matters discussed under each agenda item, the decisions made, and — most importantly — the action items with named owners and due dates. They are a concise record of what was agreed, not a transcript of everything said."},{"q":"Are meeting minutes a legal record?","a":"For boards, committees and many companies, approved minutes are an official record that can have legal and governance significance, evidencing the decisions taken and the directors''/members'' diligence. They are usually reviewed and approved (and signed by the chair) at the following meeting."},{"q":"Can I download this Meeting Minutes as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Meeting Minutes suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Meeting Minutes Generator - Free Online Meeting Minutes Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Meeting Minutes Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 2);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Business Plan Generator', 'business-plan-generator', 'Create a professional business plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional business plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"plan_title","label":"Plan Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Business Plan"},{"name":"plan_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"executive_summary","label":"Executive Summary","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This business plan summarises our company, the opportunity we are pursuing, our products and services, our market and competition, our strategy, our team and our financial projections. It is intended to guide our execution and to inform investors and partners."},{"name":"company_overview","label":"Company Overview","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe the company, its mission and vision, legal structure, location and current stage."},{"name":"products_services","label":"Products & Services","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe what you offer, the problem it solves, and your competitive advantage."},{"name":"market_analysis","label":"Market Analysis","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe your target market, its size and trends, your customers, and the competitive landscape."},{"name":"marketing_sales","label":"Marketing & Sales Strategy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Explain how you will reach customers, your pricing, channels and sales approach."},{"name":"operations_team","label":"Operations & Management Team","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe how the business runs day to day and introduce the key people and their relevant experience."},{"name":"financial_plan","label":"Financial Plan & Projections","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise your revenue model, key assumptions, funding requirements and financial projections."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What sections does a professional business plan need?","a":"A complete business plan includes an executive summary, company overview, products and services, market and competitor analysis, marketing and sales strategy, operations and management team, and a financial plan with projections. Investors and lenders internationally expect this structure, with the executive summary doing the heavy lifting."},{"q":"How long should a business plan be?","a":"Long enough to cover each section credibly but no longer — typically 15–30 pages plus financial appendices, with a one-to-two page executive summary that can stand alone. Clarity, realistic assumptions and evidence matter far more than length."},{"q":"Can I download this Business Plan as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Business Plan suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Business Plan Generator - Free Online Business Plan Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Business Plan Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 3);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Memo Generator', 'memo-generator', 'Create a professional memo online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional memo online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company / Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"memo_to","label":"To","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"memo_from","label":"From","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"memo_cc","label":"CC","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"memo_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"subject","label":"Subject","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"body","label":"Memo Body","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This memo is to inform you of the matter set out below. Please review it and take any action indicated. Should you have any questions, please contact the sender directly."},{"name":"action_required","label":"Action Required","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Clearly state any action recipients must take and by when."},{"name":"signatory_name","label":"Signatory Name","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"signatory_signature","label":"Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What is the correct format for a business memo?","a":"A business memo uses a clear header — To, From, CC, Date and Subject — followed by a concise body that states the purpose, gives the necessary detail, and specifies any action required and deadline. Memos are for internal communication and should be brief, direct and professional."},{"q":"When should I use a memo instead of an email or letter?","a":"Use a memo for formal internal announcements, policy changes or records that may need to be filed or referenced later. Letters are generally for external recipients, while memos communicate clearly and on the record within an organisation."},{"q":"Can I download this Memo as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Memo suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Memo Generator - Free Online Memo Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Memo Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 4);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Policy Document Generator', 'policy-document-generator', 'Create a professional policy document online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional policy document online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"policy_title","label":"Policy Title","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"policy_number","label":"Policy Number","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"version","label":"Version","type":"text","required":false,"default":"1.0"},{"name":"effective_date","label":"Effective Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"policy_owner","label":"Policy Owner / Department","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"purpose","label":"Purpose","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This policy sets out the company''s position and requirements on the matter described, to ensure consistent, compliant and responsible conduct across the organisation."},{"name":"scope","label":"Scope","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This policy applies to the people, roles and activities described here."},{"name":"policy_statement","label":"Policy Statement","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"The company''s policy is as set out below. All those within scope are required to understand and comply with it."},{"name":"responsibilities","label":"Responsibilities","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Define who is responsible for implementing, monitoring and enforcing this policy."},{"name":"compliance","label":"Compliance & Consequences","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Explain how compliance is monitored and the consequences of non-compliance, in line with company procedures and applicable law."},{"name":"approved_by","label":"Approved By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"approved_signature","label":"Approval Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a company policy document include?","a":"A clear policy states its purpose and scope, the policy statement itself, the responsibilities for implementing and enforcing it, and the consequences of non-compliance — all version-controlled with an effective date and approval. This structure works for HR, IT, health-and-safety, data-protection and other corporate policies."},{"q":"How should policies be approved and communicated?","a":"Policies should be approved by an appropriate authority, given a version number and effective date, communicated to everyone within scope, and reviewed periodically. Keeping a record that staff have read and understood key policies supports compliance and helps defend against disputes."},{"q":"Can I download this Policy Document as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Policy Document suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Policy Document Generator - Free Online Policy Document Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Policy Document Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 5);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Vendor Agreement Generator', 'vendor-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional vendor agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional vendor agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"vendor","label":"Vendor","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"client","label":"Client","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"scope_of_supply","label":"Scope of Supply","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"payment_terms","label":"Payment Terms","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"start_date","label":"Start Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"end_date","label":"End Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"change_request_clause","label":"Change Requests","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Any changes to the scope described in this Agreement must be agreed in writing by both parties, including any associated adjustments to fees or timelines, before such changes take effect."},{"name":"insurance_clause","label":"Insurance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where applicable, each party shall maintain insurance coverage appropriate to its obligations under this Agreement and shall provide proof of such coverage upon the other party''s reasonable request."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"vendor_signature","label":"Vendor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"client_signature","label":"Client Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Vendor Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the vendor agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the vendor agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Vendor Agreement Generator - Free Online Vendor Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Vendor Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 6);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Inventory List Generator', 'inventory-list-generator', 'Create a professional inventory list online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional inventory list online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"list_title","label":"List Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Inventory List"},{"name":"inventory_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"location","label":"Location / Warehouse","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"inventory_items","label":"Inventory Items","type":"line_items","required":true,"has_unit":true},{"name":"notes","label":"Notes","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This inventory records the items, quantities and values held at the location and date stated. Quantities have been physically verified against records where indicated."},{"name":"verified_by","label":"Verified By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"verified_signature","label":"Verification Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should an inventory list record?","a":"An inventory list records each item with its code/description, quantity on hand, unit value and total value, plus the location and date. Accurate inventory records underpin reliable accounts, efficient reordering, and audit and insurance requirements."},{"q":"Why perform and document physical inventory counts?","a":"Periodic physical counts reconcile what is actually on hand against your records, surfacing shrinkage, damage or errors. A dated, signed inventory record supports your financial statements and is frequently required by auditors and insurers."},{"q":"Can I download this Inventory List as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Inventory List suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Inventory List Generator - Free Online Inventory List Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Inventory List Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 7);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Risk Assessment Generator', 'risk-assessment-generator', 'Create a professional risk assessment online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional risk assessment online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"organization_name","label":"Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"assessment_title","label":"Assessment Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Risk Assessment"},{"name":"activity_assessed","label":"Activity / Area Assessed","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"assessment_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"assessor_name","label":"Assessor Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"scope","label":"Scope & Context","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This assessment identifies the hazards/risks associated with the activity or area described, evaluates their likelihood and impact, and sets out the controls required to reduce them to an acceptable level."},{"name":"risk_items","label":"Identified Risks (Likelihood / Impact / Controls)","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"control_measures","label":"Control Measures & Actions","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise the controls and actions required, who is responsible, and by when, to bring each risk to an acceptable level."},{"name":"review_date","label":"Review Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"approved_by","label":"Approved By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"assessor_signature","label":"Assessor Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What is the standard approach to a risk assessment?","a":"The internationally recognised approach is to identify the hazards or risks, evaluate each by likelihood and impact, decide and implement control measures to reduce them to an acceptable level, assign owners and timescales, and review periodically. Documenting this is a legal requirement for workplace health and safety in many jurisdictions."},{"q":"How often should a risk assessment be reviewed?","a":"Review whenever circumstances change — new activities, equipment, incidents or regulations — and at planned intervals (commonly annually). Recording a review date and keeping previous versions evidences that risk is being actively managed."},{"q":"Can I download this Risk Assessment as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Risk Assessment suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Risk Assessment Generator - Free Online Risk Assessment Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Risk Assessment Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 8);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Internal Audit Report Generator', 'internal-audit-report-generator', 'Create a professional internal audit report online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional internal audit report online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"organization_name","label":"Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"report_title","label":"Report Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Internal Audit Report"},{"name":"audit_area","label":"Area / Process Audited","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"audit_period_from","label":"Audit Period From","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"audit_period_to","label":"Audit Period To","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"report_date","label":"Report Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"auditor_name","label":"Auditor Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"objectives_scope","label":"Objectives & Scope","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This audit was carried out to provide independent assurance over the area described, assessing the adequacy and effectiveness of controls against the relevant policies, standards and risks."},{"name":"findings","label":"Findings & Observations","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"recommendations","label":"Recommendations","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"For each finding, a recommendation and a recommended priority are provided, together with the management response and the owner and target date for the agreed action."},{"name":"overall_opinion","label":"Overall Audit Opinion","type":"select","required":false,"options":["Satisfactory","Generally Satisfactory","Needs Improvement","Unsatisfactory"],"default":"Generally Satisfactory"},{"name":"approved_by","label":"Reviewed / Approved By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"auditor_signature","label":"Auditor Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should an internal audit report contain?","a":"A professional audit report sets out the objectives and scope, the findings and observations (with evidence and risk rating), clear recommendations, management''s response with owners and dates, and an overall opinion. This structure aligns with internationally recognised internal-audit standards (such as those of the IIA)."},{"q":"How should audit findings be prioritised?","a":"Rate each finding by risk (for example high/medium/low) based on its likelihood and potential impact, so management can focus on what matters most. Agreeing an owner and target date for each recommended action turns the report into measurable improvement."},{"q":"Can I download this Internal Audit Report as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Internal Audit Report suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Internal Audit Report Generator - Free Online Internal Audit Report Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Internal Audit Report Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 9);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Company Letterhead Generator', 'company-letterhead-generator', 'Create a professional company letterhead online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional company letterhead online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"tagline","label":"Tagline / Slogan","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"address","label":"Address","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"phone","label":"Phone","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"email","label":"Email","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"website","label":"Website","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"registration_number","label":"Company Registration No.","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"tax_number","label":"Tax / VAT Number","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"body","label":"Letter Body","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Compose your letter content here. This professionally branded letterhead applies your company identity automatically to the page."},{"name":"signatory_name","label":"Signatory Name","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"signatory_title","label":"Signatory Title","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"signatory_signature","label":"Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a professional letterhead include?","a":"A professional letterhead carries your company name and logo, a tagline if you use one, full contact details (address, phone, email, website) and — where required — your company registration and tax/VAT numbers. Consistent letterhead reinforces your brand and is often a legal requirement on formal company correspondence."},{"q":"Are company registration and VAT numbers required on letterhead?","a":"In several jurisdictions (for example the UK and parts of the EU) limited companies must show their registered name, number and registered office on business letters and order forms. Include your registration and tax/VAT numbers to stay compliant and to look credible to customers and suppliers."},{"q":"Can I download this Company Letterhead as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Company Letterhead suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Company Letterhead Generator - Free Online Company Letterhead Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Company Letterhead Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 10);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (8, 'Non-Compete Agreement Generator', 'non-compete-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional non-compete agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional non-compete agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"disclosing_party","label":"Company / Disclosing Party","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"restricted_party","label":"Restricted Party","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"restricted_activities","label":"Restricted Activities","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"geographic_scope","label":"Geographic Scope","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"duration","label":"Duration","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"disclosing_party_signature","label":"Company Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"restricted_party_signature","label":"Restricted Party Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Non-Compete Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the non-compete agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the non-compete agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Non-Compete Agreement Generator - Free Online Non-Compete Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Non-Compete Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 11);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Marketing Plan Generator', 'marketing-plan-generator', 'Create a professional marketing plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional marketing plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company / Brand","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"plan_title","label":"Plan Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Marketing Plan"},{"name":"period","label":"Plan Period","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"plan_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"executive_summary","label":"Executive Summary","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This marketing plan sets out our goals, target audience, positioning, strategy and budget for the period, together with how we will measure success."},{"name":"market_situation","label":"Market Situation & SWOT","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise the current market, key trends, and the brand''s strengths, weaknesses, opportunities and threats."},{"name":"target_audience","label":"Target Audience & Positioning","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Define the target segments, their needs, and how the brand is positioned to serve them better than the alternatives."},{"name":"objectives","label":"Marketing Objectives","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"State specific, measurable marketing objectives for the period (for example awareness, leads, conversion or retention targets)."},{"name":"strategy_channels","label":"Strategy & Channels","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe the strategy and the mix of channels (digital, content, social, paid, PR, events) you will use to reach the objectives."},{"name":"budget","label":"Budget & Activities","type":"line_items","required":true,"has_unit":true},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"kpis","label":"KPIs & Measurement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Define the key performance indicators and how and when results will be reviewed."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a marketing plan include?","a":"A solid marketing plan covers the market situation and SWOT, the target audience and positioning, specific measurable objectives, the strategy and channel mix, a budget tied to activities, and the KPIs used to measure success. Linking every activity to an objective and a metric is what separates a plan from a wish list."},{"q":"How is a marketing plan different from a marketing strategy?","a":"A strategy is the high-level approach — who you target and how you position and win; a plan turns that strategy into specific objectives, activities, budget, timeline and metrics. This template captures both, with the strategy framing the detailed plan."},{"q":"Can I download this Marketing Plan as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Marketing Plan suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Marketing Plan Generator - Free Online Marketing Plan Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Marketing Plan Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 1);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Press Release Generator', 'press-release-generator', 'Create a professional press release online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional press release online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company / Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"headline","label":"Headline","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"subheadline","label":"Sub-headline","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"release_location","label":"Dateline (City, Country)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"release_date","label":"Release Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"release_timing","label":"Release Timing","type":"select","required":false,"options":["FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE","EMBARGOED UNTIL"],"default":"FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE"},{"name":"body","label":"Body","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Lead paragraph: summarise the news — who, what, when, where and why it matters — in the first sentence. Follow with supporting detail, context and a representative quote. Keep it factual, newsworthy and concise."},{"name":"quote","label":"Spokesperson Quote","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Include a quote from a named spokesperson that adds insight or emotion, with their name and title."},{"name":"boilerplate","label":"About the Company (Boilerplate)","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"A short standard paragraph about the company — what it does, who it serves and any notable facts — used at the end of every release."},{"name":"media_contact","label":"Media Contact (Name, Email, Phone)","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What is the correct structure for a press release?","a":"A professional press release leads with a release line (e.g. ''FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE''), a strong headline and dateline, then an inverted-pyramid body: the key news in the first paragraph (who, what, when, where, why), supporting detail, a spokesperson quote, a company boilerplate, and media-contact details. Keep it factual and newsworthy — journalists ignore marketing fluff."},{"q":"How long should a press release be?","a":"Aim for one page (around 300–500 words). Put the most important, newsworthy information first so an editor can grasp the story immediately, and make it easy to quote directly. Include a clear media contact so journalists can follow up."},{"q":"Can I download this Press Release as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Press Release suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Press Release Generator - Free Online Press Release Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Press Release Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 2);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Social Media Content Calendar Generator', 'social-media-content-calendar-generator', 'Create a professional social media content calendar online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional social media content calendar online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"brand_name","label":"Brand / Account","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"calendar_title","label":"Calendar Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Social Media Content Calendar"},{"name":"period_from","label":"Period From","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"period_to","label":"Period To","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"goals","label":"Goals & Themes","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise the objectives and content themes for this period (for example awareness, engagement, product launches or seasonal campaigns)."},{"name":"platforms","label":"Platforms","type":"text","required":false,"default":"e.g. Instagram, LinkedIn, X, Facebook, TikTok, YouTube"},{"name":"content_items","label":"Scheduled Posts (Date / Platform / Content)","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"hashtags_notes","label":"Hashtags & Notes","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"List recurring hashtags, handles to tag, and any approval or asset notes."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Why use a social media content calendar?","a":"A content calendar plans what you will post, when and on which platform, so your output is consistent, on-strategy and aligned to campaigns and key dates. It prevents last-minute scrambles, improves quality through planning, and makes it easy to coordinate approvals and assets across a team."},{"q":"What should each calendar entry include?","a":"Each entry should show the date and time, the platform, the content or caption, the asset or link required, any hashtags or tags, and the post''s status (draft, approved, scheduled, published). Tying posts to themes and goals keeps the calendar strategic rather than random."},{"q":"Can I download this Social Media Content Calendar as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Social Media Content Calendar suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Social Media Content Calendar Generator - Free Online Social Media Content Calendar Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Social Media Content Calendar Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 3);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Brand Style Guide Generator', 'brand-style-guide-generator', 'Create a professional brand style guide online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional brand style guide online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"brand_name","label":"Brand Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"guide_title","label":"Guide Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Brand Style Guide"},{"name":"version","label":"Version","type":"text","required":false,"default":"1.0"},{"name":"guide_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"brand_overview","label":"Brand Overview","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise the brand''s mission, vision, personality and values — the foundation that every visual and verbal decision should reinforce."},{"name":"logo_usage","label":"Logo Usage","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Explain correct logo usage: clear space, minimum size, approved variations, and what must never be done to the logo."},{"name":"color_palette","label":"Colour Palette","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Define the primary and secondary colours with their HEX, RGB and CMYK values, and guidance on when to use each."},{"name":"typography","label":"Typography","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Specify the brand typefaces for headings and body text, with sizes, weights and usage rules."},{"name":"imagery_voice","label":"Imagery & Tone of Voice","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe the photography/illustration style and the brand''s tone of voice, with do''s and don''ts."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a brand style guide cover?","a":"A complete brand guide covers the brand''s overview and personality, logo usage rules, the colour palette (with HEX/RGB/CMYK values), typography, and imagery and tone-of-voice guidelines. It keeps every team member, agency and partner consistent across every touchpoint."},{"q":"Why is brand consistency important?","a":"Consistent use of logo, colour, type and voice makes a brand instantly recognisable and trustworthy. A documented style guide protects that consistency as your team grows and you work with external designers, printers and partners."},{"q":"Can I download this Brand Style Guide as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Brand Style Guide suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Brand Style Guide Generator - Free Online Brand Style Guide Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Brand Style Guide Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 4);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Sponsorship Proposal Generator', 'sponsorship-proposal-generator', 'Create a professional sponsorship proposal online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional sponsorship proposal online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"organization_name","label":"Your Organization / Event","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"proposal_title","label":"Proposal Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Sponsorship Proposal"},{"name":"proposal_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"sponsor","label":"Prepared For (Prospective Sponsor)","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"opportunity_overview","label":"Opportunity Overview","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This proposal invites your organisation to partner with us as a sponsor. It describes the opportunity, the audience you will reach, the benefits to your brand, and the sponsorship packages available."},{"name":"audience_reach","label":"Audience & Reach","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe the audience the sponsor will reach — size, demographics, channels and engagement — with evidence where possible."},{"name":"packages","label":"Sponsorship Packages & Benefits","type":"line_items","required":true,"has_unit":true},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"activation","label":"Activation & Deliverables","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Explain how the sponsorship will be activated and the specific deliverables and visibility the sponsor will receive."},{"name":"response_by","label":"Please Respond By","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"contact","label":"Contact (Name, Email, Phone)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"prepared_signature","label":"Authorized Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What makes a compelling sponsorship proposal?","a":"A compelling proposal sells the value to the sponsor, not just your need for funds: it quantifies the audience and reach, spells out the brand benefits and activation, offers clear tiered packages with pricing, and makes it easy to say yes. Lead with what the sponsor gains and back it with evidence."},{"q":"How should sponsorship packages be structured?","a":"Offer a small number of clearly differentiated tiers (for example bronze, silver, gold) with escalating visibility and benefits and transparent pricing. Tiered packages let sponsors self-select at the level that fits their budget and goals, and increase the average value of deals."},{"q":"Can I download this Sponsorship Proposal as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Sponsorship Proposal suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Sponsorship Proposal Generator - Free Online Sponsorship Proposal Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Sponsorship Proposal Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 5);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Influencer Agreement Generator', 'influencer-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional influencer agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional influencer agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"brand","label":"Brand","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"influencer","label":"Influencer","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"deliverables","label":"Deliverables","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"compensation","label":"Compensation","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"start_date","label":"Start Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"end_date","label":"End Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"terms","label":"Terms","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"change_request_clause","label":"Change Requests","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Any changes to the scope described in this Agreement must be agreed in writing by both parties, including any associated adjustments to fees or timelines, before such changes take effect."},{"name":"insurance_clause","label":"Insurance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where applicable, each party shall maintain insurance coverage appropriate to its obligations under this Agreement and shall provide proof of such coverage upon the other party''s reasonable request."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"brand_signature","label":"Brand Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"influencer_signature","label":"Influencer Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Influencer Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the influencer agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the influencer agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Influencer Agreement Generator - Free Online Influencer Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Influencer Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 6);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Email Marketing Campaign Brief Generator', 'email-marketing-campaign-brief-generator', 'Create a professional email marketing campaign brief online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional email marketing campaign brief online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"brand_name","label":"Brand / Company","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"campaign_name","label":"Campaign Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"brief_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"objective","label":"Campaign Objective","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"State the single primary objective of this campaign (for example nurture leads, drive sales, re-engage, announce) and the metric that defines success."},{"name":"target_audience","label":"Target Audience / Segment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Define the list segment(s) this campaign targets and why."},{"name":"send_dates","label":"Send Date(s) / Schedule","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"subject_line","label":"Subject Line(s)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"key_message","label":"Key Message & Offer","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Describe the core message, the value proposition and any offer or incentive."},{"name":"call_to_action","label":"Primary Call to Action","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"content_outline","label":"Content Outline","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Outline the email structure — hook, body, proof, CTA — and any assets required."},{"name":"kpis","label":"Success Metrics (KPIs)","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Define the KPIs (open rate, click rate, conversions, revenue) and targets used to judge the campaign."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should an email campaign brief include?","a":"A focused email brief defines a single objective and success metric, the target segment, the key message and offer, the subject line and primary call to action, the schedule, and the KPIs. Aligning everyone on one objective before writing produces sharper, higher-converting campaigns."},{"q":"How do I improve email open and click rates?","a":"Segment your list so the message is relevant, write a clear benefit-led subject line, keep one primary call to action, and personalise where you can. Define your target open/click/conversion rates in the brief and test subject lines and send times to improve over time — while respecting consent and unsubscribe rules under laws like GDPR and CAN-SPAM."},{"q":"Can I download this Email Marketing Campaign Brief as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Email Marketing Campaign Brief suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Email Marketing Campaign Brief Generator - Free Online Email Marketing Campaign Brief Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Email Marketing Campaign Brief Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 7);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Market Research Report Generator', 'market-research-report-generator', 'Create a professional market research report online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional market research report online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"organization_name","label":"Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"report_title","label":"Report Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Market Research Report"},{"name":"report_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"executive_summary","label":"Executive Summary","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This report summarises the research objectives, methodology, key findings and recommendations for the market or question studied."},{"name":"objectives_methodology","label":"Objectives & Methodology","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"State the research objectives and describe the methodology — sources, sample, methods and any limitations — so the findings can be judged on their merits."},{"name":"key_findings","label":"Key Findings","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"market_analysis","label":"Market Analysis & Insights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Analyse the findings: market size and trends, customer needs and behaviour, and the competitive landscape."},{"name":"recommendations","label":"Recommendations","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Set out clear, actionable recommendations that follow from the findings, with their expected impact."},{"name":"approved_by","label":"Approved By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a market research report contain?","a":"A credible research report states the objectives and methodology (so readers can judge reliability), presents the key findings with evidence, analyses what they mean for the market and customers, and ends with clear, actionable recommendations. Transparency about method and limitations is what makes the conclusions trustworthy."},{"q":"Why document the research methodology?","a":"Documenting the sources, sample and methods lets decision-makers weigh how much confidence to place in the findings and allows the research to be repeated or built upon. Hiding the method undermines credibility; stating it — including limitations — strengthens it."},{"q":"Can I download this Market Research Report as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Market Research Report suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Market Research Report Generator - Free Online Market Research Report Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Market Research Report Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 8);
