 to the advertising agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the advertising agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Advertising Agreement Generator - Free Online Advertising Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Advertising Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 9);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Event Marketing Plan Generator', 'event-marketing-plan-generator', 'Create a professional event marketing plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional event marketing plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"organization_name","label":"Organization","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"event_name","label":"Event Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"event_type","label":"Event Type","type":"select","required":false,"options":["Conference","Webinar","Product Launch","Trade Show","Workshop","Networking","Other"],"default":"Conference"},{"name":"event_date","label":"Event Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"venue","label":"Venue / Platform","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"objectives","label":"Objectives & Target Audience","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"State what the event aims to achieve (awareness, leads, sales, community) and who it is for."},{"name":"promotion_strategy","label":"Promotion Strategy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe how you will promote the event across channels (email, social, paid, partners, PR) and the timeline of activity."},{"name":"budget","label":"Budget & Logistics","type":"line_items","required":true,"has_unit":true},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"run_of_show","label":"Run of Show / Agenda","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Outline the event programme and key timings."},{"name":"success_metrics","label":"Success Metrics","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Define how success will be measured (registrations, attendance, leads, engagement, ROI)."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should an event marketing plan cover?","a":"A complete event plan covers the objectives and audience, the promotion strategy and timeline across channels, the budget and logistics, the run of show, and the metrics used to judge success. Tying promotion and spend to clear objectives and KPIs is what turns an event into measurable marketing ROI."},{"q":"How far in advance should I promote an event?","a":"It depends on scale, but begin promotion several weeks to a few months ahead for larger events, with a build-up of reminders as the date approaches. Map the promotion timeline in the plan so no channel or reminder is missed and registrations build steadily."},{"q":"Can I download this Event Marketing Plan as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Event Marketing Plan suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Event Marketing Plan Generator - Free Online Event Marketing Plan Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Event Marketing Plan Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 10);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Case Study Generator', 'case-study-generator', 'Create a professional case study online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional case study online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Your Company","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"case_study_title","label":"Case Study Title","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"client_name","label":"Client / Subject","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"industry","label":"Industry","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"publish_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"challenge","label":"The Challenge","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Describe the client''s situation and the specific challenge or goal they faced before working with you."},{"name":"solution","label":"The Solution","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Explain what you did — your approach, the work delivered and why it suited the challenge."},{"name":"results","label":"The Results","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Present the outcomes, quantified wherever possible (metrics, percentages, time or cost saved), to demonstrate real impact."},{"name":"testimonial","label":"Client Testimonial","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Include a short, authentic quote from the client describing their experience and the results."},{"name":"call_to_action","label":"Call to Action","type":"text","required":false,"default":"Encourage the reader to take the next step (e.g. get in touch, book a demo)."}]}', '[{"q":"What is the best structure for a marketing case study?","a":"The proven structure is Challenge → Solution → Results: describe the client''s problem, explain what you did, and prove the impact with quantified results, reinforced by a genuine client testimonial and a call to action. Specific numbers and a real customer voice make a case study persuasive."},{"q":"How do I make a case study credible?","a":"Use a real, named client where possible, quantify the results with concrete metrics, and include a direct testimonial. Specificity builds trust — ''38% more qualified leads in three months'' is far more convincing than ''significantly improved results''."},{"q":"Can I download this Case Study as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Case Study suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Case Study Generator - Free Online Case Study Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Case Study Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 11);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Pitch Deck Outline Generator', 'pitch-deck-outline-generator', 'Create a professional pitch deck outline online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional pitch deck outline online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company / Startup Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"tagline","label":"One-line Pitch","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"outline_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"problem","label":"Problem","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Describe the real, painful problem your startup solves and who suffers from it."},{"name":"solution","label":"Solution","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Explain your solution and why it is compelling and better than the alternatives."},{"name":"market","label":"Market Opportunity","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Size the market (TAM/SAM/SOM) and the trends that make now the right time."},{"name":"product","label":"Product","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe the product, its current stage and what makes it defensible."},{"name":"business_model","label":"Business Model","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Explain how you make money — pricing, unit economics and channels."},{"name":"traction","label":"Traction","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Show evidence of momentum — users, revenue, growth, partnerships or pipeline."},{"name":"competition","label":"Competition","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Map the competitive landscape and your differentiation."},{"name":"team","label":"Team","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Introduce the founders and key team and why you are the right people to win."},{"name":"ask","label":"The Ask","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"State how much you are raising, on what terms, and how you will use the funds to hit the next milestones."}]}', '[{"q":"What slides does an investor pitch deck need?","a":"A standard investor deck covers: problem, solution, market opportunity, product, business model, traction, competition, team, and the ask (how much you''re raising and use of funds). This outline gives you each section so you can tell a clear, compelling story in around 10–12 slides."},{"q":"What do investors look for most in a pitch?","a":"Investors look for a large problem, a compelling and defensible solution, evidence of traction, attractive unit economics, and a team that can execute. Clarity and proof beat hype — quantify the market and your traction, and be specific about how the raise drives the next milestones."},{"q":"Can I download this Pitch Deck Outline as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Pitch Deck Outline suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Pitch Deck Outline Generator - Free Online Pitch Deck Outline Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Pitch Deck Outline Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 1);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Business Model Canvas Generator', 'business-model-canvas-generator', 'Create a professional business model canvas online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional business model canvas online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company / Startup","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"canvas_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Business Model Canvas"},{"name":"canvas_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"value_propositions","label":"Value Propositions","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"What core value do you deliver to customers, and which problem do you solve or need do you satisfy?"},{"name":"customer_segments","label":"Customer Segments","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Who are your most important customers and segments?"},{"name":"channels","label":"Channels","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"How do you reach and deliver to customers (marketing, sales and distribution channels)?"},{"name":"customer_relationships","label":"Customer Relationships","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"What type of relationship does each segment expect (self-service, personal, community, automated)?"},{"name":"revenue_streams","label":"Revenue Streams","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"How and for what do customers pay, and what is the pricing model?"},{"name":"key_resources","label":"Key Resources","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"What key assets (people, technology, IP, capital) does your model require?"},{"name":"key_activities","label":"Key Activities","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"What key activities must you perform well to deliver your value proposition?"},{"name":"key_partnerships","label":"Key Partnerships","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Who are your key partners and suppliers, and what do they provide?"},{"name":"cost_structure","label":"Cost Structure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"What are the most important costs in your model, and which are fixed or variable?"}]}', '[{"q":"What is the Business Model Canvas?","a":"The Business Model Canvas is an internationally used one-page framework that maps the nine building blocks of a business: value propositions, customer segments, channels, customer relationships, revenue streams, key resources, key activities, key partnerships and cost structure. It gives founders and teams a shared, at-a-glance view of how the business creates, delivers and captures value."},{"q":"Why use a canvas instead of a long business plan?","a":"A canvas is fast to create, easy to iterate, and forces clarity on the essentials and how they fit together. It is ideal for early-stage exploration and pivots; you can develop a detailed business plan once the model is validated."},{"q":"Can I download this Business Model Canvas as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Business Model Canvas suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Business Model Canvas Generator - Free Online Business Model Canvas Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Business Model Canvas Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 2);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Term Sheet Generator', 'term-sheet-generator', 'Create a professional term sheet online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional term sheet online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"document_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Term Sheet"},{"name":"term_sheet_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"investor","label":"Investor","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"company","label":"Company","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"investment_amount","label":"Investment Amount","type":"number","required":true},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"instrument","label":"Instrument","type":"text","required":false,"default":"Preferred Equity / SAFE / Convertible Note"},{"name":"pre_money_valuation","label":"Pre-Money Valuation","type":"number","required":false},{"name":"equity_percentage","label":"Equity / Ownership","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"key_terms","label":"Key Terms","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Set out the principal economic and control terms — valuation, option pool, liquidation preference, anti-dilution, board composition, voting and protective provisions, and information rights — as the basis for definitive documents."},{"name":"conditions","label":"Conditions & Exclusivity","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe conditions to closing (due diligence, legal documentation, approvals) and any exclusivity/no-shop period."},{"name":"binding_clause","label":"Binding / Non-Binding","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except for the confidentiality, exclusivity and governing-law provisions, this term sheet is a non-binding expression of intent and does not create a legally binding obligation to invest, which arises only on signing definitive agreements."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false,"default":"This document shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the applicable jurisdiction stated by the parties."},{"name":"investor_signature","label":"Investor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"company_signature","label":"Company Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is a term sheet legally binding?","a":"Most term sheets are largely non-binding — they record the key terms the parties intend to put into definitive agreements — except for specific provisions that are usually binding, such as confidentiality, exclusivity/no-shop and governing law. The template makes this binding/non-binding split explicit, which is standard international practice."},{"q":"What key terms does a venture term sheet cover?","a":"Typical terms include the investment amount and instrument, pre-money valuation and resulting ownership, the option pool, liquidation preference, anti-dilution protection, board composition, voting and protective provisions, and information rights. These shape the economics and control of the deal, so review them with experienced counsel before signing."},{"q":"Can I download this Investment Term Sheet as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Investment Term Sheet suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Term Sheet Generator - Free Online Term Sheet Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Term Sheet Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 3);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Founders Agreement Generator', 'founders-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional founders agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional founders agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"business_name","label":"Business Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"founder_one","label":"Founder One","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"founder_two","label":"Founder Two","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"founders","label":"Full Founder Roster","type":"group_list","required":false,"columns":[{"name":"name","label":"Founder Name","type":"text"},{"name":"role","label":"Role / Title","type":"text"},{"name":"equity_percentage","label":"Equity %","type":"text"}]},{"name":"roles_responsibilities","label":"Roles & Responsibilities","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"vesting_terms","label":"Vesting Terms","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"non_compete_clause","label":"Non-Compete","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where legally permitted, each party agrees not to engage in any business directly competing with the other party''s business within the same market for a reasonable period following termination of this Agreement, to the extent enforceable under applicable law."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"founder_one_signature","label":"Founder One Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"founder_two_signature","label":"Founder Two Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Founders Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the founders agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the founders agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Founders Agreement Generator - Free Online Founders Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Founders Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 4);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Cap Table Generator', 'cap-table-generator', 'Create a professional cap table online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional cap table online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"table_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Capitalization Table"},{"name":"as_of_date","label":"As of Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"total_shares","label":"Total Shares Issued","type":"number","required":false},{"name":"shareholders","label":"Shareholders & Holdings","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"option_pool","label":"Option Pool / Convertibles","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"notes","label":"Notes","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This capitalization table summarises the ownership of the company as of the date stated, including issued shares, the option pool and any convertible instruments. Percentages are calculated on the basis indicated (issued or fully diluted)."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What is a cap table and why does it matter?","a":"A capitalization (cap) table records who owns what in a company — founders, investors, and the option pool — with share counts and ownership percentages. It is essential for fundraising, option grants and exits, and investors will scrutinise it, so keeping it accurate and up to date is critical from day one."},{"q":"What is the difference between issued and fully diluted ownership?","a":"Issued ownership is based on shares actually issued today; fully diluted ownership also counts options, warrants and convertible instruments as if exercised or converted. Investors usually negotiate on a fully diluted basis, so state clearly which basis your percentages use."},{"q":"Can I download this Capitalization Table as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Capitalization Table suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Cap Table Generator - Free Online Cap Table Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Cap Table Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 5);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Investor Update Generator', 'investor-update-generator', 'Create a professional investor update online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional investor update online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"update_period","label":"Update Period (e.g. Month/Quarter)","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"update_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"highlights","label":"Highlights & Lowlights","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Open with the key wins and the key challenges since the last update — investors value candour about both."},{"name":"key_metrics","label":"Key Metrics (KPI / This Period / Change)","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"financials","label":"Financial Summary","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise revenue, burn, cash on hand and runway so investors can see the financial picture at a glance."},{"name":"progress","label":"Product & Team Progress","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe progress on product, customers, hiring and partnerships since the last update."},{"name":"asks","label":"Asks / How You Can Help","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Tell investors specifically how they can help — intros, hiring, advice — investors are a resource, not just a reporting line."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a regular investor update include?","a":"A good investor update shares highlights and lowlights, the key metrics with their change, a financial summary (revenue, burn, cash and runway), progress on product and team, and specific asks. Regular, candid updates build trust, keep investors engaged, and make it easier to raise your next round."},{"q":"How often should startups send investor updates?","a":"Monthly or quarterly is typical. Consistency matters more than frequency — pick a cadence you can sustain, be honest about challenges as well as wins, and always include clear asks so investors can actively help."},{"q":"Can I download this Investor Update as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Investor Update suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Investor Update Generator - Free Online Investor Update Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Investor Update Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 6);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Executive Summary Generator', 'executive-summary-generator', 'Create a professional executive summary online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional executive summary online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"document_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Executive Summary"},{"name":"summary_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"overview","label":"Company Overview","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Introduce the company in a sentence or two — what you do, for whom, and why it matters."},{"name":"problem_solution","label":"Problem & Solution","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"State the problem you solve and your solution, clearly and concisely."},{"name":"market","label":"Market Opportunity","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise the market size and opportunity."},{"name":"business_model","label":"Business Model","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Explain briefly how the business makes money."},{"name":"traction","label":"Traction & Milestones","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Highlight key achievements and momentum to date."},{"name":"team","label":"Team","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Introduce the key people and why they can execute."},{"name":"financials_ask","label":"Financials & Ask","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise the financial highlights or projections and, if raising, the funding ask and use of funds."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What is an executive summary and why is it important?","a":"An executive summary is a concise, standalone overview of a business or plan — covering the company, problem and solution, market, model, traction, team and financial ask — written so a busy reader can grasp the essentials in a minute. It is often the only part investors or partners read first, so it must earn the deeper read."},{"q":"How long should an executive summary be?","a":"Keep it to one page (or two at most). Lead with the most compelling points, write in plain, confident language, and make sure it stands on its own without the full document. Edit ruthlessly — every sentence should add value."},{"q":"Can I download this Executive Summary as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Executive Summary suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Executive Summary Generator - Free Online Executive Summary Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Executive Summary Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 7);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Letter of Intent Generator', 'letter-of-intent-generator', 'Create a professional letter of intent online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional letter of intent online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"document_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Letter of Intent"},{"name":"loi_date","label":"Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"party_a","label":"Party A","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"party_b","label":"Party B","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"purpose","label":"Purpose / Proposed Transaction","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"This Letter of Intent sets out the parties'' mutual intention to proceed with the proposed transaction or relationship described below, and the principal terms on which they intend to negotiate definitive agreements in good faith."},{"name":"key_terms","label":"Principal Terms","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Summarise the key proposed terms — scope, price/consideration, structure, timeline and key conditions — as the basis for the definitive agreement."},{"name":"due_diligence","label":"Due Diligence & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Describe any due diligence, approvals or conditions that must be satisfied before the parties enter into binding agreements."},{"name":"exclusivity_period","label":"Exclusivity Period","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"binding_clause","label":"Binding / Non-Binding","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except for the provisions on confidentiality, exclusivity, costs and governing law, this Letter of Intent is a non-binding statement of intent and does not create any binding obligation to complete the transaction, which arises only on signing definitive agreements."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false,"default":"This document shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the applicable jurisdiction stated by the parties."},{"name":"party_a_signature","label":"Party A Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"party_b_signature","label":"Party B Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is a letter of intent legally binding?","a":"A letter of intent is generally non-binding as to the main transaction — it records the parties'' intention and the principal terms they will negotiate in good faith — while certain clauses (confidentiality, exclusivity, costs, governing law) are usually binding. The template states this split clearly. Careful wording matters, because poorly drafted LOIs can unintentionally create binding obligations."},{"q":"When should I use a letter of intent?","a":"Use an LOI to record serious intent and the headline terms before investing in full due diligence and definitive contracts — common in acquisitions, investments, partnerships and major commercial deals. It aligns the parties and can secure exclusivity while the detailed agreement is negotiated."},{"q":"Can I download this Letter of Intent as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Letter of Intent suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Letter of Intent Generator - Free Online Letter of Intent Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Letter of Intent Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 8);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Equity Vesting Agreement Generator', 'equity-vesting-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional equity vesting agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional equity vesting agreement online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"business_name","label":"Business Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"company_representative","label":"Company Representative","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"grantee","label":"Grantee","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"total_shares","label":"Total Shares","type":"number","required":false},{"name":"start_date","label":"Vesting Start Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"vesting_period","label":"Vesting Period","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"cliff_period","label":"Cliff Period","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"company_representative_signature","label":"Company Representative Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"grantee_signature","label":"Grantee Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Equity Vesting Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the equity vesting agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the equity vesting agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Equity Vesting Agreement Generator - Free Online Equity Vesting Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Equity Vesting Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 9);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (10, 'Startup Budget Plan Generator', 'startup-budget-plan-generator', 'Create a professional startup budget plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional startup budget plan online in minutes — fill in the details, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-rocket-takeoff', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company / Startup","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"plan_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Startup Budget Plan"},{"name":"budget_period_from","label":"Period From","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"budget_period_to","label":"Period To","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"starting_cash","label":"Starting Cash / Funding","type":"number","required":false},{"name":"revenue_projections","label":"Projected Revenue","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"expenses","label":"Projected Expenses","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"assumptions","label":"Key Assumptions","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Document the assumptions behind your revenue and cost projections (growth rate, pricing, headcount, conversion) so the budget can be understood and stress-tested."},{"name":"runway_note","label":"Burn Rate & Runway","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Summarise your monthly net burn and the resulting runway (how many months your cash lasts), and the milestones you aim to reach before needing more funding."},{"name":"prepared_by","label":"Prepared By","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a startup budget plan include?","a":"A startup budget plan projects revenue and expenses over a period, states the starting cash, and — crucially — calculates burn rate and runway (how many months the cash lasts). Documenting the assumptions lets you and investors stress-test the numbers and plan the next raise around clear milestones."},{"q":"What is burn rate and runway, and why do they matter?","a":"Burn rate is how much cash your startup spends net each month; runway is how many months your remaining cash will last at that burn. They are the single most important numbers for an early-stage startup — they tell you how long you have to hit the milestones needed for the next round or profitability."},{"q":"Can I download this Startup Budget Plan as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Startup Budget Plan suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Startup Budget Plan Generator - Free Online Startup Budget Plan Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Startup Budget Plan Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 10);
