may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"change_request_clause","label":"Change Requests","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Any changes to the scope described in this Agreement must be agreed in writing by both parties, including any associated adjustments to fees or timelines, before such changes take effect."},{"name":"insurance_clause","label":"Insurance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where applicable, each party shall maintain insurance coverage appropriate to its obligations under this Agreement and shall provide proof of such coverage upon the other party''s reasonable request."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"company_representative_signature","label":"Company Representative Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"advisor_signature","label":"Advisor Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Advisory Board Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the advisory board agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I download the advisory board agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."},{"q":"Can I email the document directly to my client?","a":"Yes, Pro and Premium users can send any generated document as a PDF or DOCX email attachment directly from Invoxaco."}]', 1, 1, 'Advisory Board Agreement Generator - Free Online Advisory Board Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Generate a Advisory Board Agreement Generator online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word. No design skills needed.', 11);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (4, 'CV / Resume Generator', 'cv-resume-generator', 'Build a professional CV or resume online in minutes — add your experience and education, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Build a professional CV or resume online in minutes — add your experience and education, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-people', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"full_name","label":"Full Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"headline","label":"Professional Headline","type":"text","required":false,"default":"Results-driven professional"},{"name":"email","label":"Email","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"phone","label":"Phone","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"location","label":"Location","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"linkedin","label":"LinkedIn / Portfolio URL","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"summary","label":"Professional Summary","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"A concise, achievement-focused summary of your experience, key skills and the value you bring, tailored to the role you are applying for."},{"name":"work_experience","label":"Work Experience","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"education","label":"Education","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"skills","label":"Key Skills","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"List your most relevant technical and soft skills, separated by commas."},{"name":"certifications","label":"Certifications & Awards","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"languages","label":"Languages","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"references","label":"References","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Available on request."}]}', '[{"q":"How do I make my CV stand out to international employers?","a":"Lead with a tailored professional summary, quantify achievements (not just duties), match keywords to the job description, keep formatting clean and consistent, and keep it to one or two pages. This template produces a clean, ATS-friendly layout that works for applications in the US, UK, EU and beyond."},{"q":"What is the difference between a CV and a resume?","a":"In the US a ''resume'' is a concise one-to-two page summary, while a ''CV'' is a longer academic document. In the UK, EU and much of the world ''CV'' simply means the standard job-application document. This generator produces a professional, internationally accepted format for either use."},{"q":"Can I download this CV / Resume as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this CV / Resume suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'CV / Resume Generator - Free Online CV / Resume Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional CV or resume online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and download as PDF or Word.', 12);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (4, 'Salary Slip Generator', 'salary-slip-generator', 'Create a professional salary slip / payslip online in minutes — add earnings and deductions, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional salary slip / payslip online in minutes — add earnings and deductions, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-people', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"payslip_title","label":"Title","type":"text","required":true,"default":"Salary Slip"},{"name":"employee_name","label":"Employee Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"employee_id","label":"Employee ID","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"designation","label":"Designation","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"department","label":"Department","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"pay_period","label":"Pay Period","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"pay_date","label":"Pay Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"currency","label":"Currency","type":"text","required":false,"default":"USD"},{"name":"days_worked","label":"Days / Hours Worked","type":"number","required":false},{"name":"bank_account","label":"Bank Account (last 4 digits)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"earnings","label":"Earnings","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"deductions","label":"Deductions","type":"line_items","required":true},{"name":"notes","label":"Notes","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This payslip is a computer-generated statement of earnings and deductions for the stated pay period. Please retain it for your records."}]}', '[{"q":"What should a compliant salary slip (payslip) show?","a":"A payslip should show the employer and employee details, the pay period, gross earnings broken down (basic, allowances, overtime), itemised deductions (tax, social security/insurance, pension), and the net pay. In many countries (e.g. the UK and most of the EU) providing an itemised payslip is a legal requirement."},{"q":"Can I show multiple earnings and deduction lines?","a":"Yes. Add a line for each earning (basic salary, allowances, bonuses) and each deduction (income tax, social-security/insurance, loan repayments). The gross, total deductions and net pay are presented clearly for the employee."},{"q":"Can I download this Salary Slip as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Salary Slip suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Salary Slip Generator - Free Online Salary Slip Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a salary slip or payslip online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word.', 13);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (9, 'Company Profile Generator', 'company-profile-generator', 'Create a professional company profile online in minutes — showcase your mission, products, and achievements, then download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional company profile online in minutes — showcase your mission, products, and achievements, then download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-megaphone', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"company_name","label":"Company Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"tagline","label":"Tagline","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"founded_year","label":"Founded Year","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"industry","label":"Industry","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"company_overview","label":"Company Overview","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"mission_statement","label":"Mission Statement","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"vision_statement","label":"Vision Statement","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"core_values","label":"Core Values","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"products_services","label":"Products & Services","type":"group_list","required":false,"columns":[{"name":"name","label":"Name","type":"text"},{"name":"category","label":"Category","type":"text"},{"name":"description","label":"Description","type":"textarea"}]},{"name":"why_choose_us","label":"Why Choose Us","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"clients_achievements","label":"Clients & Achievements","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"contact_details","label":"Contact Details","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"website","label":"Website","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"social_media","label":"Social Media","type":"text","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What should a professional company profile include?","a":"A strong company profile presents your company name and branding, an overview and mission, your history and milestones, products and services, your team or leadership, key clients or achievements, and contact details. It is used in proposals, tenders, investor and partner meetings, so a polished, complete profile builds immediate credibility."},{"q":"How is a company profile different from a business plan?","a":"A company profile is an outward-facing introduction to who you are and what you offer, used for marketing and relationships; a business plan is an internal/investor document detailing strategy and financial projections. This generator focuses on a professional, presentation-ready company profile."},{"q":"Can I download this Company Profile as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Company Profile suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Company Profile Generator - Free Online Company Profile Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional company profile online free with Invoxaco. Fill a simple form, preview instantly, and export as PDF or Word.', 12);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'SaaS Agreement Generator', 'saas-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional SaaS subscription agreement online in minutes — define the platform, subscription terms, and service level commitment, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional SaaS subscription agreement online in minutes — define the platform, subscription terms, and service level commitment, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-cloud-check', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"provider","label":"Service Provider","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"subscriber","label":"Subscriber / Client","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"service_description","label":"SaaS Platform / Service Description","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"subscription_plan","label":"Subscription Plan / Tier","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"subscription_fee","label":"Subscription Fee","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"billing_cycle","label":"Billing Cycle","type":"select","required":false,"options":["Monthly","Quarterly","Annually","One-Time"]},{"name":"start_date","label":"Start Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"end_date","label":"End Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"uptime_sla","label":"Service Level / Uptime Commitment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Provider will use commercially reasonable efforts to maintain at least 99.5% platform uptime, excluding scheduled maintenance."},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"change_request_clause","label":"Change Requests","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Any changes to the scope described in this Agreement must be agreed in writing by both parties, including any associated adjustments to fees or timelines, before such changes take effect."},{"name":"insurance_clause","label":"Insurance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where applicable, each party shall maintain insurance coverage appropriate to its obligations under this Agreement and shall provide proof of such coverage upon the other party''s reasonable request."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"provider_signature","label":"Service Provider Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"subscriber_signature","label":"Subscriber Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the SaaS Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to the SaaS agreement tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I customize the subscription and service level terms?","a":"Yes, every field including subscription fees, billing cycle, and the uptime commitment can be edited to match your specific SaaS offering."},{"q":"Does the document include standard legal clauses?","a":"Yes. The generator includes generic confidentiality, data protection, liability, and termination clauses you can edit, plus a Governing Law field for your jurisdiction."}]', 1, 1, 'SaaS Agreement Generator - Free Online SaaS Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional SaaS subscription agreement online in minutes — define the platform, subscription terms, and service level commitment, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 13);
