s Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"developer_signature","label":"Developer Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"client_signature","label":"Client Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Software Development Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I specify custom deliverables and milestones?","a":"Yes, the Deliverables field is fully editable so you can list source code, documentation, milestones, or any other project-specific output."},{"q":"Who owns the intellectual property created under this agreement?","a":"The generator includes an editable Intellectual Property Rights clause so you can specify whether the client, the developer, or both share ownership of the resulting work."}]', 1, 1, 'Software Development Agreement Generator - Free Online Software Development Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional software development agreement online in minutes — define project scope, deliverables, and payment terms, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 14);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Software License Agreement Generator', 'software-license-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional software license agreement online in minutes — define the licensed software, license type, and fees, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional software license agreement online in minutes — define the licensed software, license type, and fees, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-key', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"licensor","label":"Licensor","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"licensee","label":"Licensee","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"software_description","label":"Software Description","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"license_type","label":"License Type","type":"select","required":false,"options":["Single User","Multi-User / Site License","Perpetual License","Subscription License","Open Source / Royalty-Free"]},{"name":"license_fee","label":"License Fee","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"start_date","label":"Start Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"end_date","label":"End Date (leave blank for perpetual)","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"licensor_signature","label":"Licensor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"licensee_signature","label":"Licensee Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Software License Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I create a perpetual license with this generator?","a":"Yes, select ''Perpetual License'' as the license type and leave the end date blank."},{"q":"Does this generator cover SaaS subscriptions too?","a":"For ongoing hosted software subscriptions we recommend the dedicated SaaS Agreement Generator, which includes uptime and service-level fields."}]', 1, 1, 'Software License Agreement Generator - Free Online Software License Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional software license agreement online in minutes — define the licensed software, license type, and fees, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 15);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Website Development Agreement Generator', 'website-development-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional website development agreement online in minutes — define project scope, deliverables, and payment terms, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional website development agreement online in minutes — define project scope, deliverables, and payment terms, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-window', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"developer","label":"Web Developer / Agency","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"client","label":"Client","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"project_description","label":"Website Project Description","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"deliverables","label":"Deliverables","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Website source code, design files, and basic documentation upon final payment."},{"name":"payment_terms","label":"Payment Terms","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"start_date","label":"Start Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"end_date","label":"End Date","type":"date","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"change_request_clause","label":"Change Requests","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Any changes to the scope described in this Agreement must be agreed in writing by both parties, including any associated adjustments to fees or timelines, before such changes take effect."},{"name":"insurance_clause","label":"Insurance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where applicable, each party shall maintain insurance coverage appropriate to its obligations under this Agreement and shall provide proof of such coverage upon the other party''s reasonable request."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"developer_signature","label":"Developer Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"client_signature","label":"Client Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Website Development Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Does it cover hosting and maintenance after launch?","a":"You can describe ongoing hosting or maintenance terms in the Deliverables or Additional Terms fields, or use a separate Retainer Agreement for ongoing maintenance work."},{"q":"Can I download the agreement as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create can be exported as a print-ready PDF, and Pro/Premium plans can also export an editable DOCX file."}]', 1, 1, 'Website Development Agreement Generator - Free Online Website Development Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional website development agreement online in minutes — define project scope, deliverables, and payment terms, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 16);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Mutual NDA Generator', 'mutual-non-disclosure-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional mutual non-disclosure agreement online in minutes — protect confidential information shared by both parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional mutual non-disclosure agreement online in minutes — protect confidential information shared by both parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-shield-lock', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"party_one","label":"First Party","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"party_two","label":"Second Party","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"purpose","label":"Purpose of Disclosure","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"term_years","label":"Term (Years)","type":"number","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"party_one_signature","label":"First Party Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"party_two_signature","label":"Second Party Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"How is a Mutual NDA different from a standard NDA?","a":"A standard NDA protects information disclosed by one party; a mutual NDA protects confidential information shared by both parties equally."},{"q":"Is the Mutual NDA Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I set how long the confidentiality obligations last?","a":"Yes, use the Term (Years) field to specify how long the confidentiality obligations remain in effect after signing."}]', 1, 1, 'Mutual NDA Generator - Free Online Mutual NDA Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional mutual non-disclosure agreement online in minutes — protect confidential information shared by both parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 17);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'IP Assignment Agreement Generator', 'ip-assignment-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional IP assignment agreement online in minutes — transfer ownership of intellectual property between parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional IP assignment agreement online in minutes — transfer ownership of intellectual property between parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-lightbulb', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"assignor","label":"Assignor","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"assignee","label":"Assignee","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"ip_description","label":"Description of Assigned Intellectual Property","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"consideration","label":"Consideration / Payment","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"assignor_signature","label":"Assignor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"assignee_signature","label":"Assignee Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"What types of IP can be assigned with this agreement?","a":"The agreement is written generically so it can cover patents, trademarks, copyrighted works, trade secrets, or other intellectual property — describe the specific IP in the description field."},{"q":"Is the IP Assignment Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Does the assignment need to be for payment?","a":"No, you can leave the consideration field blank or note ''for no consideration'' if the assignment is gratuitous."}]', 1, 1, 'IP Assignment Agreement Generator - Free Online IP Assignment Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional IP assignment agreement online in minutes — transfer ownership of intellectual property between parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 18);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Copyright Transfer Agreement Generator', 'copyright-transfer-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional copyright transfer agreement online in minutes — transfer ownership of a copyrighted work between parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional copyright transfer agreement online in minutes — transfer ownership of a copyrighted work between parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-c-circle', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"transferor","label":"Transferor","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"transferee","label":"Transferee","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"work_description","label":"Description of Copyrighted Work","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"consideration","label":"Consideration / Payment","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"transferor_signature","label":"Transferor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"transferee_signature","label":"Transferee Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Copyright Transfer Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"What kinds of works can this agreement cover?","a":"Describe any copyrighted work in the Description field — written content, artwork, photography, music, software, or other creative works."},{"q":"Does this transfer moral rights too?","a":"Moral rights treatment varies by jurisdiction; describe any specific moral rights terms in the Additional Terms field and consult an attorney if this matters for your situation."}]', 1, 1, 'Copyright Transfer Agreement Generator - Free Online Copyright Transfer Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional copyright transfer agreement online in minutes — transfer ownership of a copyrighted work between parties, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 19);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Joint Venture Agreement Generator', 'joint-venture-agreement-generator', 'Create a professional joint venture agreement online in minutes — define the venture''s purpose, contributions, and profit split, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional joint venture agreement online in minutes — define the venture''s purpose, contributions, and profit split, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-diagram-3', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"agreement_date","label":"Agreement Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"venture_name","label":"Joint Venture Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"partner_one","label":"First Partner","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"partner_two","label":"Second Partner","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"purpose","label":"Purpose of the Joint Venture","type":"textarea","required":true},{"name":"capital_contribution","label":"Capital / Asset Contributions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"profit_split","label":"Profit & Loss Split","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"background","label":"Background / Recitals","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement is entered into between the parties for the purpose described herein. Each party confirms that it has the full right, power, and authority to enter into this Agreement and to perform its obligations under it."},{"name":"confidentiality_clause","label":"Confidentiality","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to keep confidential all non-public information disclosed by the other party in connection with this Agreement, including trade secrets, customer data, financial information, and business processes, and shall not disclose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"non_compete_clause","label":"Non-Compete","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where legally permitted, each party agrees not to engage in any business directly competing with the other party''s business within the same market for a reasonable period following termination of this Agreement, to the extent enforceable under applicable law."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"partner_one_signature","label":"First Partner Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"partner_two_signature","label":"Second Partner Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Joint Venture Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"How is a joint venture different from a partnership?","a":"A joint venture is typically formed for a specific project or limited purpose, while a partnership is usually an ongoing business relationship — though the documents share many similar clauses."},{"q":"Can more than two partners use this agreement?","a":"This generator is built for two-party ventures. For ventures with more partners, use the Multi-Partner Agreement Generator instead."}]', 1, 1, 'Joint Venture Agreement Generator - Free Online Joint Venture Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional joint venture agreement online in minutes — define the venture''s purpose, contributions, and profit split, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 20);
