lose such information to any third party without prior written consent, except as required by law."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"warranty_clause","label":"Warranty","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Except as expressly stated in this Agreement, each party provides its performance on an as-is basis with a limited warranty that services and deliverables will be performed in a professional and workmanlike manner consistent with industry standards."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"indemnification_clause","label":"Indemnification","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless the other party from and against any third-party claims, damages, losses, or expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of its breach of this Agreement, negligence, or willful misconduct."},{"name":"force_majeure_clause","label":"Force Majeure","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party shall be liable for any failure or delay in performance due to causes beyond its reasonable control, including acts of war, natural disasters, government restrictions, or internet or utility outages."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"dispute_resolution_clause","label":"Dispute Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"non_compete_clause","label":"Non-Compete","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where legally permitted, each party agrees not to engage in any business directly competing with the other party''s business within the same market for a reasonable period following termination of this Agreement, to the extent enforceable under applicable law."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"principal_signature","label":"Principal Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"agent_signature","label":"Agent Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Commission Agreement Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Can I define tiered commission rates?","a":"Yes, describe tiered or sliding-scale commission rates in the Commission Structure & Rates field."},{"q":"Does this cover commission on renewals or recurring revenue?","a":"Yes, specify renewal or recurring commission terms in the Commission Structure & Rates or Additional Terms fields."}]', 1, 1, 'Commission Agreement Generator - Free Online Commission Agreement Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional commission agreement online in minutes — define commission structure, products, and payment terms, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 24);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Terms of Service Generator', 'terms-of-service-generator', 'Create a professional Terms of Service page online in minutes — covers user accounts, acceptable use, IP, liability, and termination, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional Terms of Service page online in minutes — covers user accounts, acceptable use, IP, liability, and termination, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-file-text', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"effective_date","label":"Effective Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"company","label":"Company / Website Operator","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"website_name","label":"Website / Service Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"acceptance_of_terms","label":"Acceptance of Terms","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"By accessing or using this website or service, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the service."},{"name":"user_accounts","label":"User Accounts","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Users may be required to create an account to access certain features. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activity that occurs under your account."},{"name":"acceptable_use","label":"Acceptable Use","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"You agree not to use the service for any unlawful purpose, to infringe the rights of others, to transmit harmful code, or to interfere with the operation of the service."},{"name":"intellectual_property_clause","label":"Intellectual Property Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party retains all rights, title, and interest in its pre-existing intellectual property. Ownership of any new intellectual property created specifically under this Agreement shall be as agreed in writing between the parties; absent such agreement, each party retains ownership of its own contributions."},{"name":"disclaimer_of_warranties","label":"Disclaimer of Warranties","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The service is provided as is and as available without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement."},{"name":"liability_clause","label":"Limitation of Liability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, neither party''s total liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall exceed the total fees paid or payable under this Agreement in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim, except for liability arising from gross negligence, willful misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations."},{"name":"termination_clause","label":"Termination","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Either party may terminate this Agreement for convenience by providing thirty (30) days'' written notice to the other party. Either party may terminate immediately upon the other party''s material breach that remains uncured for fifteen (15) days after written notice, or upon the other party''s insolvency or bankruptcy."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"changes_to_terms","label":"Changes to These Terms","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised terms."},{"name":"contact_information","label":"Contact Information","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us using the details provided on our website."}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Terms of Service Generator free to use?","a":"Yes, every Invoxaco plan includes access to this tool. Free plan documents are watermarked and limited to 10 per month; Pro and Premium plans remove the watermark and raise or remove the limit."},{"q":"Do I need to sign a Terms of Service page?","a":"No, Terms of Service are a unilateral policy published by the website or service operator, not a document signed by both parties — there is no signature section."},{"q":"Does this replace legal review?","a":"No. This generator produces a generic, editable starting point. Businesses with specific regulatory obligations should have the final terms reviewed by a qualified attorney."}]', 1, 1, 'Terms of Service Generator - Free Online Terms of Service Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional Terms of Service page online in minutes — covers user accounts, acceptable use, IP, liability, and termination, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 25);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Privacy Policy Generator', 'privacy-policy-generator', 'Create a professional Privacy Policy online in minutes — covers data collection, usage, sharing, security, and user rights, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional Privacy Policy online in minutes — covers data collection, usage, sharing, security, and user rights, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-incognito', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"effective_date","label":"Effective Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"company","label":"Company / Website Operator","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"website_name","label":"Website / Service Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"information_collected","label":"Information We Collect","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, contact details, and usage data when you interact with our website or service."},{"name":"how_information_is_used","label":"How We Use Your Information","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We use the information we collect to provide and improve our services, communicate with you, process transactions, and comply with legal obligations."},{"name":"cookies_tracking","label":"Cookies & Tracking","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience. See our Cookie Policy for further details."},{"name":"data_sharing","label":"Data Sharing & Third Parties","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with trusted service providers who assist in operating our business, subject to confidentiality obligations, or as required by law."},{"name":"data_security","label":"Data Security","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures designed to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction."},{"name":"user_rights","label":"Your Rights","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict the use of your personal data under applicable laws such as the GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA. Contact us to exercise these rights."},{"name":"childrens_privacy","label":"Children''s Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Our service is not directed to children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children."},{"name":"changes_to_policy","label":"Changes to This Policy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page with an updated effective date."},{"name":"contact_information","label":"Contact Information","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us using the details provided on our website."}]}', '[{"q":"Does this privacy policy help with GDPR and CCPA compliance?","a":"The template is structured around the disclosures expected by major privacy laws including the EU/UK GDPR and the California CCPA/CPRA — what personal data you collect, the purposes and legal basis, sharing, retention, security, and the rights of data subjects. Complete each section accurately for your business and, for regulated or high-risk processing, have it reviewed by a privacy professional."},{"q":"Where should I display my privacy policy?","a":"Publish it at a stable URL linked from your website footer, app stores, sign-up and checkout forms, and anywhere you collect personal data. Many laws and platforms (Apple, Google, ad networks) require an accessible, up-to-date privacy policy."},{"q":"Can I download this Privacy Policy as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Privacy Policy suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Privacy Policy Generator - Free Online Privacy Policy Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional Privacy Policy online in minutes — covers data collection, usage, sharing, security, and user rights, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 26);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Cookie Policy Generator', 'cookie-policy-generator', 'Create a professional Cookie Policy online in minutes — explain what cookies your site uses and how visitors can manage them, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional Cookie Policy online in minutes — explain what cookies your site uses and how visitors can manage them, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-cookie', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"effective_date","label":"Effective Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"company","label":"Company / Website Operator","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"website_name","label":"Website / Service Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"what_are_cookies","label":"What Are Cookies","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website. They help the website remember information about your visit, such as preferences and login status."},{"name":"types_of_cookies_used","label":"Types of Cookies We Use","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We use essential cookies required for the website to function, performance cookies to understand how visitors use our site, and functionality cookies to remember your preferences."},{"name":"third_party_cookies","label":"Third-Party Cookies","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Some cookies may be placed by third-party services we use, such as analytics or advertising partners. These third parties have their own privacy and cookie policies."},{"name":"managing_cookies","label":"Managing Cookies","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling certain cookies may affect the functionality of our website."},{"name":"changes_to_policy","label":"Changes to This Policy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page with an updated effective date."},{"name":"contact_information","label":"Contact Information","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact us using the details provided on our website."}]}', '[{"q":"Do I legally need a cookie policy and consent banner?","a":"If your website uses cookies or similar technologies and you have visitors in the EU/UK, the ePrivacy rules and GDPR require clear information about cookies and, for non-essential cookies, prior consent. A cookie policy explaining the categories and purposes of cookies is the standard way to meet this transparency obligation."},{"q":"What should a cookie policy explain?","a":"It should describe the types of cookies used (strictly necessary, performance, functional, targeting), their purpose and duration, any third-party cookies, and how users can manage or withdraw consent through their browser or your preferences tool."},{"q":"Can I download this Cookie Policy as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Cookie Policy suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Cookie Policy Generator - Free Online Cookie Policy Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional Cookie Policy online in minutes — explain what cookies your site uses and how visitors can manage them, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 27);
INSERT INTO document_templates (category_id, name, slug, short_description, description, icon, plan_required, fields_schema, faqs, is_built, is_active, meta_title, meta_description, sort_order) VALUES (3, 'Refund Policy Generator', 'refund-policy-generator', 'Create a professional Refund Policy online in minutes — define eligibility, process, and timeframes for refunds, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'Create a professional Refund Policy online in minutes — define eligibility, process, and timeframes for refunds, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 'bi-arrow-counterclockwise', 'free', '{"fields":[{"name":"effective_date","label":"Effective Date","type":"date","required":true},{"name":"company","label":"Company / Business","type":"party","required":true},{"name":"business_name","label":"Business Name","type":"text","required":true},{"name":"refund_eligibility","label":"Refund Eligibility","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"Customers may request a refund within the timeframe stated below if the product or service did not meet the description provided, or as otherwise required by applicable consumer protection law."},{"name":"refund_process","label":"How to Request a Refund","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"To request a refund, contact us using the details below with your order or invoice number and the reason for the request. We will review and respond within a reasonable time."},{"name":"refund_timeframe","label":"Refund Timeframe","type":"text","required":false,"default":"5-10 business days"},{"name":"non_refundable_items","label":"Non-Refundable Items / Exceptions","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Certain products or services may be non-refundable, including custom or personalized work, downloadable digital products once accessed, and services already substantially performed."},{"name":"contact_information","label":"Contact Information","type":"textarea","required":true,"default":"If you have any questions about this Refund Policy, please contact us using the details provided on our website."}]}', '[{"q":"What makes a refund policy enforceable and fair?","a":"A clear refund policy states what can be returned or refunded, the time window, the condition of goods, who pays return shipping, and how and when refunds are issued. In the EU/UK consumers also have statutory cancellation rights for many distance sales, which your policy should respect as a minimum."},{"q":"Where should I display my refund policy?","a":"Show it before purchase — on product pages, at checkout, and in order confirmations — and link it from your website footer. Clear, accessible refund terms reduce disputes and chargebacks and are required by most payment providers and marketplaces."},{"q":"Can I download this Refund Policy as PDF and Word?","a":"Yes. Every document you create on Invoxaco can be exported as a polished, print-ready PDF, and Pro and Premium plans can also download a fully editable Microsoft Word (DOCX) file."},{"q":"Is this Refund Policy suitable for use in the US, UK, EU and other countries?","a":"The template uses clear, internationally accepted business language and a neutral structure that works across the United States, United Kingdom, European Union and most other jurisdictions. Set the governing law or jurisdiction field to your country, and for high-value or regulated matters have a local professional review the final document."},{"q":"Can I add my company logo, branding and signature?","a":"Yes. Add your logo, brand colour, authorised signature and company stamp once in your settings and they are applied automatically to this and every other document you generate."}]', 1, 1, 'Refund Policy Generator - Free Online Refund Policy Generator | Invoxaco', 'Create a professional Refund Policy online in minutes — define eligibility, process, and timeframes for refunds, preview instantly, and download as PDF or DOCX.', 28);
